<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>HTML To Node</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9dc56;
      color: #F9F9DC;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #00e5ff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #400040;
      border: 3px solid #9ACBD0;
      text-align: justify;
      padding: 40px 70px;
      background-color: #f9f9dc28;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease;
    }

    p:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 9, 9, 0.1);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

     header {
      background-color: #48A6A7;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-bottom: 13%;
    }

    header nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.5s;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      color: black;
    } 

    button {
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #218838;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('head') %>

    <h1>Welcome To My Website</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nesciunt quidem veritatis esse ea dolores deleniti saepe dicta. Magnam excepturi, veniam quae quis sapiente voluptas aspernatur nemo hic praesentium. Dolorum, numquam..
    </p>
</body>

</html>